    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_3594028665" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3594028665" />
    <a title="Zainab" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/67918882-zainab"><img alt="Zainab" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1635792126p2/67918882.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3594028665?book_show_action=true">Oct 13, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Zainab" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Zainab" href="/user/show/67918882-zainab">Zainab</a>
      </span>

          added it




        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3594028665" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3344844008037302707">Dawson comes from a very difficult background and falls in love with Amanda, she comes from a rich family. They spend a wonderful time together and their love grows deeper every day. An accident separates their paths. A few years later, they meet again and realize, that their love is still as deep as it was in the past. But Amanda&apos;s life now, revolves around very different things and so she cannot stay with him. But with the help of a stroke of fate, they still remain connected, even if it&apos;s a v</span>
  <span id="freeText3344844008037302707" style="display:none">Dawson comes from a very difficult background and falls in love with Amanda, she comes from a rich family. They spend a wonderful time together and their love grows deeper every day. An accident separates their paths. A few years later, they meet again and realize, that their love is still as deep as it was in the past. But Amanda's life now, revolves around very different things and so she cannot stay with him. But with the help of a stroke of fate, they still remain connected, even if it's a very strange way. As always the book is heartbreaking. I find the story around Dawson and Amanda very close, the other stories are important for the story, but they seemed a bit prudish to me, so the actual story (Dawson and Amanda) could have been more extended. <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="3344844008037302707" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


